                      anonymousClass,
                      "org_slf4j/jcl_over_slf4j/missing-simplelog.properties"
              );
  
              assertThat(action.run()).isNull();
          } catch (Error error) {
              if (!NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(error)) {
                  throw error;
              }
          }
      }
  
